### Yeni görev ekle
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot projesini tamamla",
  "description": "DTO, validation ve hata yönetimini bitir",
  "dueDate": "2026-07-30"
}

### Bütün görevleri listele
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks

### ID ile görev getir
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

### Görev güncelle
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring Boot projesini güncelle",
  "description": "Proje kodlarını kontrol et",
  "dueDate": "2026-08-01"
}

### Tamamlandı olarak işaretle
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1/complete

### Tamamlanmadı olarak işaretle
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1/pending

### Tamamlanan görevleri getir
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/completed

### Bekleyen görevleri getir
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/pending

### Görev sil
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

### Hatalı validation testi
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "Bu istek hata vermelidir",
  "dueDate": "2020-01-01"
}

### Bulunmayan görev testi
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/9999